                <p>Release Candidate #5</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Updated German translations</li>
                    <li>Added Italian translations</li>
                    <li>Included translators in the credits section</li>
                    <li>Fixed various bugs and minor issues</li>
                    <li>Added new tests and enhanced existing ones</li>
                    <li>Added support for clearing cooldowns on action groups</li>
